@ratkosrb 
Prior to the server going down within the last 24 hours, the stones worked perfectly fine for the first day or two of uptime.  Once players started reporting this issue, I was able to confirm that I also could not interact with the stones, despite having used them during those first few days.

Once again, the stones are able to be interacted with now that the server has been online for only 21 hours, but I suspect they will once again be broken in a matter of time.  It appears that after a certain number of respawns, these stones become uninteractable for some reason.  The issue cannot be reproduced on a fresh server restart, or even the first X uses.  I would advise reusing the stones until an issue occurs.

