The only potential loot table setup where an item cannot drop is when it is on a table above 100%, like this item: https://github.com/slowtorta/turtlewow-bug-tracker/issues/5429

I just want to make sure that when you have moved the item to group 1 or 2 that you have reduced the other items' drop chance so that the group doesn't exceed 100%.

